        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Military Selective Service Repeal Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill repeals the requirement for males of ages 18 through 25 years old to register with the Selective Service. The bill also specifies that an individual shall not be penalized for prior failure to register with the Selective Service.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
